rows.label: qst500110_msg0002
rows.name:
Neyaya very surprise and shock to
find cave-in. Was no cave-in last time
Neyaya come here!

rows.label: qst500110_msg0003
rows.name:
Must have fallen down because of
ground going shaky-shake.

rows.label: qst500110_msg0004
rows.name:
But Neyaya take advantage!
Searching area for Linka Honey!

rows.label: qst500110_msg0005
rows.name:
If put Linka Honey into juice,
will surely become so tasty-tasty
anyone who drink it faint from happy!

rows.label: qst500110_msg0006
rows.name: But honey not easy to find...

rows.label: qst500110_msg0007
rows.name:
Friends tell Neyaya if seeing any
Linka Honey, yes? Neyaya catch faint
smell, so definitely in Cliffs somewhere!

rows.label: qst500110_msg0009
rows.name: Is that Linka Honey friends have?!

rows.label: qst500110_msg0010
rows.name: Where friends find such precious thing?

rows.label: qst500110_msg0011
rows.name:
Ohhhh... Make many sense!
Neyaya always looking in completely
different place, so never find any.

rows.label: qst500110_msg0012
rows.name: Neyaya go get honey right away!

rows.label: qst500110_msg0013
rows.name:
Oh yes, Neyaya have many brotherpons
and sisterpons also hunting for juice
ingredients.

rows.label: qst500110_msg0014
rows.name:
If friends meet them, not forget to say
hello-lo! Maybe they need helping too!
